des:
Use Alexa to voice control your Blumfeldt products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our "Blumfeldt" app in app market, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in "Blumfeldt" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable "Blumfeldt" skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on "device name".
Alexa, turn off "device name".
Alexa, what is the temperature of "device name"?
Alexa, what is the target temperature of the "device name"?
Alexa, set "device name" to twenty.
Alexa, set "device name" to N.
